---
title: Mexican Spiced Turkey Steak with Sweet Potato and Black Beans
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Turkey steak with Sweet Potato & Beans in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-spiced-turkey-steak-0b54086f-19cda475.jpg
